Debian Trixie
-------------

hping3 targets Debian Trixie only.

Install dependencies:

$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install -y build-essential libpcap-dev tcl-dev

Build and install:

$ ./configure (first try ./configure --help)
$ make
$ sudo make install

NOTE: Root access is required at runtime for raw socket operations.
For security reasons do not setuid hping3 on multiuser systems.
